title: MID LANER LOOKING FOR TEAM FOR OCEANIC OPEN
body: Like in the title mid looking for team peaked plat 3 season 4, want to play for a team during oceanic opens hit me up!

replies.body: Sure, but I'm gonna need you tell me which champs you main. I'll add you, I'm looking to get competitive, so long as you have good knowledge and communication skills I'd be willing to recruit you. ^_^
